name: Are you home yet?
description: Being a woman in Mexico means no walking late alone, being harazed while walking on the streets and basically living with fear for your life. The rate is 10 victims of feminicide per day in Mexico. We have to live with a constant survival mode and this is no life. I can only hope this will go away someday, in the meantime, I go to my camera to get the feelings out of me. It gets old to live in fear
